============================================================
       MOMENTUM SCALPER MACHINE ENGINE — WORKSPACE v2.7.1
============================================================
 Core Philosophy: Keep It Stupid Simple. Envision First.

 [SYSTEM CONTROL LIFECYCLE COMMAND]
   • start      : Boots the scalper engine daemon in the background
   • stop       : Completely terminates all running node instances safely
   • restart    : Cycles the engine (kills active process, boots fresh)
   • status     : Queries the system process table to verify active PID

 [TELEMETRY & LOG MONITORING]
   • dashboard  : Launches the LIVE web dashboard (ROI, PnL, Chart)
   • check      : Inspects the active state ledger json for positions
   • history    : Views the last 40 historical entry and exit marks
   • logs       : Streams real-time, high-frequency engine runtime data

 [AUDIT & ANALYSIS]
   • node check_status.js         : Full system health snapshot
   • node simulate_from_logs.js   : Replay log for balance verification
   • node scalper_backtest.js     : 72-hour historical backtest
   • node dump.js                 : Aggregate all source to dump.txt

 System Guardrails: 3-Min Handshake | 0.35% SL | 0.75% TP
 Logs Directory  : ./.logs/ (stderr, CaptainsLog.md, engine output)
 Archive         : ./archive/ (versioned snapshots of every release)
